sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant AGW as Agentgateway Proxy
    participant Secret as K8s Secrets (API Keys)
    participant Backend as Backend

    Client->>AGW: Request + Authorization: Bearer API-key
    AGW->>Secret: Lookup secret (by label selector or name)
    Secret-->>AGW: Secret found, compare key
    alt Key valid
        AGW->>Backend: Forward request
        Backend-->>AGW: Response
        AGW-->>Client: 200 OK
    else Key invalid
        AGW-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end
